        <Paragraph>
            This sample showcases the paging capability of SfDataGrid. Paging support is achieved by using SfDataPager control which return pages of data with entries where selection of the pages can be done using the numbered buttons. Paging loads the entire data collection to the SfDataPager and bind the PagedSource property of the SfDataPager to the ItemsSource property of SfDataGrid. 
